title: Cabal
description:
;D This is probably the best complete-free MMO I have ever seen or played.

The only difference between the paid account, and the non-paid is you get access to less-clogged serves, and a 25% increase on EXP. It&#039;s a little pricier than other MMOs for the monthly sub, but at the same time the rest of it is free. Once you get to a certain level, you could technically sell gold and shit, and you could get there in less than a month. Higher level chars have the ability to go to a "war" channel and battle the shit out of other countries.

Pretty darn cool. This is the US client. Downloaded 13-04-08.
